### Primary PhillyMUG Contact and Information
Please visit [http://www.meetup.com/Philladelphia-MongoDB-User-Group/](http://www.meetup.com/Philladelphia-MongoDB-User-Group/) for more information on the group and to find a schedule of events and meetups in and around the Philadelphia area.

### Authors and Contributors
In February of 2016, Mike Lynn (@mlynn) created this repository.
